<h2>Chickens are raised as sources of food and as pets.</h2>
<div class=”chickenbackground”>
<div class=”textbackground”>
<p>Chickens are a large part of modern society as they provide large chain restaurants with the food that a large population takes for granted every time you go to a fast food restaurant. Many people have them as pets and harvest their eggs, and many more live on farms to provide a food source for the main populace.</p>
